#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kate;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &kate;"

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. Tag: primary
#: configuring.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "configure"
msgstr "konfigurirati"

#. Tag: secondary
#: configuring.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "settings"
msgstr "nastavitve"

#. Tag: tertiary
#: configuring.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "preferences"
msgstr "preference"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; offers several means of tweaking the application to behave as "
"desired. The most important ones are:"
msgstr ""
"&kate; ponuja več načinov za prilagajanje aplikacije, da se obnaša po želji. "
"Najpomembnejši so:"

#. Tag: term
#: configuring.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Configuration Dialog"
msgstr "Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main configuration tool, allowing you to configure the &kate; "
"application, the editor component and the usage of plugins."
msgstr ""
"Glavno konfiguracijsko orodje, ki vam omogoča konfiguracijo &kate; "
"aplikacija, komponenta urejevalnika in uporaba vtičnikov."

#. Tag: term
#: configuring.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> Menu"
msgstr "Meni <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to change often used settings, and to launch the configuration "
"dialogs."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča spreminjanje pogosto uporabljenih nastavitev in zagon "
"konfiguracijskih pogovornih oken."

#. Tag: term
#: configuring.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guimenu>View</guimenu> Menu"
msgstr "Meni <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to split the current frame, as well as to display the icons and "
"line numbers pane for the currently edited document."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča razdelitev trenutnega okvira ter prikaz ikon in podokna s številkami "
"vrstic za trenutno urejen dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The embedded terminal uses the configuration defined in the "
"&systemsettings;, and may also be configured by clicking the &RMB; to "
"display a context menu."
msgstr ""
"Vgrajeni terminal uporablja konfiguracijo, določeno v &systemsettings;, "
"konfigurirati pa ga je mogoče tudi s klikom &RMB; za prikaz kontekstnega "
"menija."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main Configuration Dialog"
msgstr "Glavno pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kate; configuration dialog displays a tree of topics on the left, and a "
"configuration page corresponding to the selected topic on the right."
msgstr ""
"&kate; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno prikaže drevo tem na levi in "
"konfiguracijsko stran, ki ustreza izbrani temi, na desni."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "The configuration is divided into two groups, namely:"
msgstr "Konfiguracija je razdeljena v dve skupini, in sicer:"

#. Tag: link
#: configuring.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija aplikacije"

#. Tag: link
#: configuring.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor component configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija komponente urejevalnika"

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kate; Application Configuration"
msgstr "&kate; Konfiguracija aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "This group contains pages to configure the main &kate; application"
msgstr "Ta skupina vsebuje strani za konfiguracijo glavnega &kate; aplikacija"

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "This section contains a few global options for &kate;"
msgstr "Ta razdelek vsebuje nekaj globalnih možnosti za &kate;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Behavior"
msgstr "Vedenje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open each document in its own window"
msgstr "Odprite vsak dokument v svojem oknu"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, each document will be opened in its own window. If not enabled, "
"each document will be opened in a new tab in the current window."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, bo vsak dokument odprt v svojem oknu. Če ni omogočeno, bo "
"vsak dokument odprt v novem zavihku v trenutnem oknu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to output view upon message type"
msgstr "Preklopite na izhodni pogled glede na vrsto sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows configuring when &kate; should show an output pane "
"depending on the type of action output."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost omogoča konfiguracijo, ko &kate; mora prikazati izhodno podokno, "
"odvisno od vrste izhoda dejanja."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to choose between <guimenuitem>Never</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Error</guimenuitem> (on error), <guimenuitem>Warning</"
"guimenuitem> (on warning or above), <guimenuitem>Info</guimenuitem> (on info "
"or above), and <guimenuitem>Log</guimenuitem> (on log or above)."
msgstr ""
"Izbirate lahko med <guimenuitem>Nikoli</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Napaka</"
"guimenuitem> (ob napaki), <guimenuitem>Opozorilo</guimenuitem> (ob opozorilu "
"ali zgoraj), <guimenuitem>Informacije</guimenuitem > (na informacijah ali "
"zgoraj) in <guimenuitem>Dnevnik</guimenuitem> (na dnevniku ali zgoraj)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use a separate dialog for handling externally modified files"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite ločeno pogovorno okno za obdelavo datotek, spremenjenih od zunaj"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, &kate; will notify you with a modal dialog about all files "
"modified from outside the application whenever the main window receives "
"input focus. You will be able to deal with several modified files at once, "
"you can reload, save or discard changed files in groups."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, &kate; vas bo z modalnim pogovornim oknom obvestil o vseh "
"datotekah, spremenjenih zunaj aplikacije, kadar koli glavno okno prejme "
"fokus vnosa. Ukvarjali se boste lahko z več spremenjenimi datotekami hkrati, "
"spremenjene datoteke lahko znova naložite, shranite ali zavržete v skupinah."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If not enabled, &kate; will individually ask you what to do for each "
"modified file only when that file's view receives focus."
msgstr ""
"Če ni omogočeno, &kate; vas bo posebej vprašal, kaj storiti za vsako "
"spremenjeno datoteko šele, ko bo pogled te datoteke prejel fokus."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Open"
msgstr "Hitro odpiranje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Match Mode"
msgstr "Način ujemanja"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the list mode for the <link linkend=\"view-quick-open\">Quick Open</"
"link> tool. The files can be matched by their name or by their path."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite način seznama za orodje <link linkend=\"view-quick-open\">Hitro "
"odpiranje</link>. Datoteke se lahko ujemajo po imenu ali poti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "List Mode"
msgstr "Način seznama"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the list mode for the <link linkend=\"view-quick-open\">Quick Open</"
"link> tool. It is possible to choose from <guilabel>Current Project Files</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>All Projects Files</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite način seznama za orodje <link linkend=\"view-quick-open\">Hitro "
"odpiranje</link>. Izbirate lahko med <guilabel>trenutnimi projektnimi "
"datotekami</guilabel> in <guilabel>vsemi projektnimi datotekami</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:156 configuring.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabs"
msgstr "Zavihki"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limit number of tabs"
msgstr "Omejite število zavihkov"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the maximum number of tabs. Choose <guimenuitem>Unlimited</guimenuitem> "
"if you do not want to restrict this number."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite največje število zavihkov. Izberite <guimenuitem>Neomejeno</"
"guimenuitem>, če ne želite omejiti te številke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto hide tabs"
msgstr "Samodejno skrij zavihke"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "When checked tabs will be hidden if only one document is open."
msgstr "Ko je označeno, bodo zavihki skriti, če je odprt samo en dokument."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show close button"
msgstr "Pokaži gumb za zapiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "When checked each tab will display a close button."
msgstr "Ko je označeno, bo na vsakem zavihku prikazan gumb za zapiranje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand tabs"
msgstr "Razširite zavihke"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "When checked tabs take as much size as possible."
msgstr "Ko so označeni, zavihki zavzamejo čim večjo velikost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "Double click opens a new document"
msgstr "Dvojni klik odpre nov dokument"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "When checked double click opens a new document."
msgstr "Ko je označeno, dvojni klik odpre nov dokument."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Middle click closes a document"
msgstr "Srednji klik zapre dokument"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "When checked middle click closes a document."
msgstr "Ko je označeno, srednji klik zapre dokument."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow tab scrolling"
msgstr "Dovoli pomikanje po zavihkih"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked this will allow scrolling in tab bar when number of tabs is "
"large."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bo to omogočilo drsenje v vrstici z zavihki, ko je število "
"zavihkov veliko."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Elide tab text"
msgstr "Besedilo zavihka Elide"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "When checked tab text might be elided if its too long."
msgstr ""
"Izbriši besedilo zavihka Ko je potrjeno, bo besedilo zavihka morda "
"izbrisano, če je predolgo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backward button pressed"
msgstr "Pritisnjen gumb za nazaj"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows selecting the mouse back button action between the "
"<guimenuitem>Previous tab</guimenuitem> and the <guimenuitem>History back</"
"guimenuitem> items."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro dejanja miškinega gumba nazaj med <guimenuitem>Prejšnjim "
"zavihkom</guimenuitem> in elementoma <guimenuitem>Zgodovina nazaj</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forward button pressed"
msgstr "Pritisnjen gumb Naprej"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows selecting the mouse forward button action between the "
"<guimenuitem>Next tab</guimenuitem> and the <guimenuitem>History forward</"
"guimenuitem> items."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro dejanja miškinega gumba naprej med elementoma "
"<guimenuitem>Naslednji zavihek</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Zgodovina "
"naprej</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Session"
msgstr "Seja"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section contains options related to <link linkend=\"fundamentals-using-"
"sessions\">using sessions</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vsebuje možnosti, povezane z <link linkend=\"fundamentals-using-"
"sessions\">uporabo sej</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Startup Behavior"
msgstr "Vedenje pri zagonu aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select how you want &kate; to behave at startup. This setting can be "
"overridden by specifying what to do on the <link linkend=\"command-line-"
"options\">command line</link>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, kako želite &kate; obnašati ob zagonu. To nastavitev je mogoče "
"preglasiti tako, da v <link linkend=\"command-line-options\">ukazni vrstici</"
"link> določite, kaj storiti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start new session"
msgstr "Začni novo sejo"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this option, &kate; will start a new, unnamed session when you start "
"the application."
msgstr ""
"S to možnostjo &kate; bo začel novo, neimenovano sejo, ko zaženete "
"aplikacijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Load last-used session"
msgstr "Naloži zadnjo uporabljeno sejo"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; will use the most recently opened session at startup. This is good if "
"you want to use the same session always or switch rarely."
msgstr ""
"&kate; bo ob zagonu uporabil zadnjo odprto sejo. To je dobro, če želite "
"vedno uporabljati isto sejo ali redko preklopiti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manually choose a session"
msgstr "Ročno izberite sejo"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; will display a small dialog that lets you choose your preferred "
"session, or load the default session if none have been saved. This is the "
"default behavior. Nice if you use a lot of different sessions frequently."
msgstr ""
"&kate; prikaže majhno pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko izberete želeno sejo "
"ali naložite privzeto sejo, če nobena ni shranjena. To je privzeto vedenje. "
"Lepo, če pogosto uporabljate veliko različnih sej."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Startup/Shutdown Behavior"
msgstr "Vedenje pri zagonu/zaustavitvi aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select how you want &kate; to behave at shutdown. It is possible to define "
"what &kate; should <guilabel>Automatically save and restore</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, kako želite &kate; obnašati ob zaustavitvi. Možno je definirati, "
"kaj &kate; mora <guilabel>Samodejno shraniti in obnoviti</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "Newly-created unsaved files"
msgstr "Na novo ustvarjene neshranjene datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this item checked, &kate; will automatically save all newly-created "
"unsaved files."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ta element označen, &kate; samodejno shrani vse na novo ustvarjene "
"neshranjene datoteke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Files with unsaved changes"
msgstr "Datoteke z neshranjenimi spremembami"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item allows configuring &kate; for automatically saving all files with "
"unsaved changes on shutdown."
msgstr ""
"Ta element omogoča konfiguracijo &kate; za samodejno shranjevanje vseh "
"datotek z neshranjenimi spremembami ob zaustavitvi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close Kate entirely when the last file is closed"
msgstr "Popolnoma zaprite Kate, ko je zadnja datoteka zaprta"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &kate; will shutdown when the last file being edited is closed, "
"otherwise a blank page will open so that you can start a new file."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, &kate; se bo zaustavil, ko bo zaprta zadnja datoteka, ki "
"ste jo urejali, sicer se bo odprla prazna stran, da lahko začnete novo "
"datoteko."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Session Elements"
msgstr "Elementi seje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include window configuration"
msgstr "Vključi konfiguracijo oken"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &kate; will save the window configuration with each session."
msgstr "Če je omogočeno, &kate; bo shranil konfiguracijo okna z vsako sejo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep meta-information past sessions"
msgstr "Ohranite metainformacije preteklih sej"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, &kate; will store meta data such as bookmarks and session "
"configuration even when you close your documents. The data will be used if "
"the document is unchanged when reopened."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, &kate; bo shranil meta podatke, kot so zaznamki in "
"konfiguracija seje, tudi ko zaprete dokumente. Podatki bodo uporabljeni, če "
"bo dokument ob ponovnem odprtju nespremenjen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete unused meta-information after"
msgstr "Po tem izbrišite neuporabljene metainformacije"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the maximum number of days to keep meta information for previously "
"opened files. This helps keep the database of meta information reasonably "
"sized."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite največje število dni za shranjevanje metainformacij za predhodno "
"odprte datoteke. To pomaga ohraniti zbirko podatkov z meta informacijami "
"razumne velikosti."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any changes to the session data (opened files and, if enabled, window "
"configuration) will always be saved."
msgstr ""
"Vse spremembe podatkov seje (odprte datoteke in, če je omogočeno, "
"konfiguracija oken) bodo vedno shranjene."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Vtičniki"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page provides a list of installed plugins for the &kate; application. "
"Each plugin is represented with its name and a short description. You can "
"check the checkbox with an item to enable the plugin it represents."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani je seznam nameščenih vtičnikov za &kate; aplikacija. Vsak "
"vtičnik je predstavljen s svojim imenom in kratkim opisom. Potrditveno polje "
"ob elementu lahko potrdite, da omogočite vtičnik, ki ga predstavlja."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a plugin provides configuration options, a section to access those will "
"appear as a child of this page."
msgstr ""
"Če vtičnik nudi konfiguracijske možnosti, bo razdelek za dostop do njih "
"prikazan kot podrejeni element te strani."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about the available plugins, see <xref linkend=\"plugins"
"\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o razpoložljivih vtičnikih glejte <xref linkend=\"plugins"
"\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Editor Component Configuration"
